Package: vhs-digitizer
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: VHS Digitizer <vhs-digitizer@localhost>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip, ffmpeg, adduser
Recommends: obs-studio
Description: VHS tape digitization management application
 A locally-hosted web application for managing and tracking the conversion
 of physical VHS tape collections into digital video files. Provides a web
 interface accessible from any device on the local network, with OBS Studio
 integration for automated recording control.
